Config Cuda darknet

pip install yolov4

sudo apt-get install python3-opencv
sudo apt install libopencv-dev

Change Makefile to active cuda, cunnd and opencv
https://github.com/AlexeyAB/darknet#pre-trained-models

system config to enable cuda compile (make) 
# DARKNET
export PATH=/usr/local/cuda-11.04/bin${PATH:+:${PATH}}
export LD_LIBRARY_PATH=/usr/local/cuda-11.04/lib64${LD_LIBRARY_PATH:+:${LD_LIBRARY_PATH}}
